m the author's argument is a creative method for living within the emotional and spiritual tension that develops whenever our belief system is challenged or disrupted.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 0aPsychoanalysis and religion. 4aPsychology : Pastoral Counseling. 7aRELIGION / Faith.2bisacsh1 aJonte-Pace, Diane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978079148719840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791487198423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791487198/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles